data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Offering $5,000 seller credit! Welcome to the exquisite Foxtail Townhome nestled in the serene Pinewood Reserve! This two-story, interior townhome boasts three spacious bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and an attached 2-car garage. As you enter, you'll be greeted by an expansive gathering space on the main floor, perfect for hosting guests. This flows seamlessly into a sleek, modern kitchen equipped with top-tier stainless-steel appliances, a refrigerator, a pantry, and pristine finishes. Adding to its first-floor conveniences are a laundry room and a powder room, all laid on elegant tile flooring that extends through the main living areas and bathrooms.    Step outside to discover a private, fenced rear courtyard, an ideal spot for outdoor dining or simply enjoying the evening air. As the day winds down, head upstairs to the relaxing Owner's Suite, which features a voluminous walk-in closet and a luxurious en suite bathroom with a double sink and oversized shower. Additionally, there are two more cozy bedrooms and a secondary bathroom. For added storage, there's a thoughtful linen closet.    An added financial advantage, the loan on this townhome is assumable, potentially simplifying the buying process for the next homeowner.    What's more, this townhome is move-in ready with all appliances included, stylish window blinds, pre-wired pendant lighting, and an elegant iron spindle staircase. The Pinewood Reserve itself is a gem, set amidst 140 acres of lush conservation with swift access to FL-417. Its prime location places it minutes away from Downtown Orlando, Lake Nona, Waterford Lakes, UCF, Orlando International Airport, and more. Residents will also appreciate the close proximity to schools, shopping, and entertainment venues. Within the community, enjoy amenities such as a resort-style pool with a chic cabana and three fun-filled playgrounds. Experience the perfect blend of luxury and location by visiting the Foxtail Townhome, where every detail promises a lifestyle of elegance and convenience.
